title: Sultan Aksanov
text:
Sultan Raisovich Aksanov (; born 19 August 1993) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays as a <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> for Armenian club <a href="Sevan%20FC">Sevan FC</a>.
Club career.
Aksanov made his professional debut for <a href="FC%20Tom%20Tomsk">FC Tom Tomsk</a> on 23 April 2013 in a game against <a href="FC%20SKA-Energiya%20Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Energiya Khabarovsk</a>.
